fields.title: my kindle
fields.content: USE - As far as the reading experience, I really like the touch compared to the physical buttons on the previous generation. At first I was worried that I would constantly be turning the page from accidentally touching the screen, but this didn't become much of an issue. The screen is broken up into mapped sections, so if you touch the far left side that covers about 1" of the left of the screen, it goes to the previous page!

fields.title: Don't make the same mistake
fields.content: Don't make the same mistake I did -- the 4 GB version may seem like a good deal if you don't think you'll need a lot of space, but what they don't tell you is that some features REQUIRE an actual hard drive. You might think that a gig is a gig and it shouldn't make any difference whether it's on a disk or flash memory, but to the Xbox, they are not equivalent!

fields.title: I chose Pentax becaus
fields.content: I chose Pentax because I already have 2 Pentax SLR bodies and wanted to be able to use my lenses. I chose the K-R over the K-X based on a lot of reading and what I thought was a good fit for me (and cost, too)!

fields.content: This fabulous table will bring a contemporary feel to any room and allow for extra organization in your home by freeing up table space. The magazine rack is 12.5 Width, 5 Depth, 6.5 Height. Overall dimensions are 18 Diameter, 22 Height, 12 dome base. Assembly required.

fields.content: Impressive, eye-catching detail graces this stylish ottoman. This fabulous design is fitted with orange faux leather that's decorated with a nickel finish nailhead design. Each ottoman is uniquely hand-crafted, so no two pieces will be exactly alike. A spectacular addition to seating areas that's sure to enhance your stylish decor.

fields.content: Get a semi-custom look and fit with our 2-piece Patented Construction slipcover. Elastic corners, separate seat cushion, and wearable fabric make for a comfortable fit that transforms your old sofa or loveseat to a new one.

fields.content: The contrasting microfiber and faux leather covering of the Sundance Collection highlights this contemporary seating group. Coordinating pillows accentuate the thoroughly modern lines making Sundance the perfect addition to your home.

fields.title: Gravity Queen Platform Bed
fields.content: Finish:Ebony, Bed Size:Queen The straight and pure lines of the modern Gravity Queen Platform Bed will give your bedroom a high-end look at a great price. This simple but practical platform bed is a great value for your money, as it does not require any bedspring.
